Package org.usfirst.frc.team1072.robot.commands.auton

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutonomousCommand
    A set of commands to be called during the autonomous period.
    Delay
    Accurately delays (when in a series of sequential commands) for a given amount of time.
    FollowPath
    A command to follow a unidirectional motion profile.
    FollowPathArc
    Follows a motion profile in an arc-like manner.
    PauseUntilCommandBegins
    Pauses, when in a series of sequential commands, until (and any time after) a command begins.
    PauseUntilPathBegins
    Pauses the thread (in a series of sequential commands) until the given path begins, waiting a set amount of time either after the command begins or before it ends.
    PauseUntilReachingPosition
    Pauses a sequence of command until a given position is reached.
    PrebufferPathPoints
    Prebuffers the points in a path to improve autonomous speed.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PauseUntilPathBegins.PauseType
    The various types of pauses which this command can handle.
